      "id": "2060027488227520859",
      "text": "Smart businesses manage expectations\n\n1) Fast food sells you predictability\n\n2) Luxury raises your expectations \n\n3) Then there are the businesses that lower your expectations https://t.co/kvbslPfKbh",
