    {
      "id": "2060027077194088557",
      "text": "Airports make people feel stupid. Even smart people. They’re a prison crossed with a mall.\n\nMcDonald’s does well there. The airport degrades judgment, so people reach for the one thing that will not surprise them. Fast food. https://t.co/hEw1u5WFqN",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-28T15:55:03.000Z",
