      "id": "2060026275767447662",
      "text": "The same cup of coffee can taste bad at a luxury resort and perfectly fine at a cheap hotel. Even if the coffee didn’t change. Our expectation changed. \n\nSatisfaction = Experience + Expectation\n\nHalf of satisfaction is in our power. But we get manipulated\nhttps://t.co/qI1kDPOO9m",
